ear mate. |\\n| [GearRatioNumerator](SolidWorks.Interop.sldworks~SolidWorks.Interop.sldworks.IGearMateFeatureData~GearRatioNumerator.md \\\"GearRatioNumerator Property \\\\(IGearMateFeatureData\\\\)\\\") | Gets or sets the numerator of the gear ratio of this gear mate. |\\n| [Reverse](SolidWorks.Interop.sldworks~SolidWorks.Interop.sldworks.IGearMateFeatureData~Reverse.md \\\"Reverse Property \\\\(IGearMateFeatureData\\\\)\\\") | Gets or sets whether to change the direction of rotation of the gears relative to one another in this gear mate. |\\nTop\\n# See Also\\n# ### \\n[IGearMateFeatureData Interface](SolidWorks.Interop.sldworks~SolidWorks.Interop.sldworks.IGearMateFeatureData.md \\\"IGearMateFeatureData Interface\\\") [SolidWorks.Interop.sldworks Namespace](SolidWorks.Interop.sldworks~SolidWorks.Interop.sldworks_namespace.md \\\"SolidWorks.Interop.sldworks Namespace\\\")\"\n  }\n}"}}], "serverName": "local", "toolName": "unknown"}}, "timestamp": "2025-12-22T00:39:59.789734Z"}
{"method": "session/update", "params": {"update": {"sessionUpdate": "agent_message_chunk", "content": {"type": "text", "text": "# 齿轮配合特征数据接口属性\n\n根据查询结果，这是来自SolidWorks API的IGearMateFeatureData接口的属性信息，用于定义齿轮配合关系。以下是该接口的主要属性：\n\n## 公共属性"}}}, "timestamp": "2025-12-22T00:40:02.784817Z"}
{"method": "session/update", "params": {"update": {"sessionUpdate": "agent_message_chunk", "content": {"type": "text", "text": "\n\n| 属性名 | 描述 |\n|--------|------|\n| EntitiesToMate | 获取或设置此齿轮配合中的配合实体 |\n| GearRatioDenominator | 获取或设置此"}}}, "timestamp": "2025-12-22T00:40:03.533237Z"}
{"method": "session/update", "params": {"update": {"sessionUpdate": "agent_message_chunk", "content": {"type": "text", "text": "齿轮配合的齿轮比分母 |\n| GearRatioNumerator | 获取或设置此齿轮配合的齿轮比分子 |\n| Reverse | 获取或设置是否改变齿轮之间相对旋转方向 |\n\n这些属性主要用于在Solid"}}}, "timestamp": "2025-12-22T00:40:04.213543Z"}
{"method": "session/update", "params": {"update": {"sessionUpdate": "agent_message_chunk", "content": {"type": "text", "text": "Works软件中通过API控制齿轮配合关系，包括指定参与配合的实体、设定齿轮传动比以及控制旋转方向。\n\n这与您之前提到的齿轮计算器项目不同，这是专门针对SolidWorks三维建模软件中齿轮配合功能的API"}}}, "timestamp": "2025-12-22T00:40:05.403041Z"}
